&lt;h3 id=&quot;cornerness-measure&quot;&gt;Cornerness Measure&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cornerness measure &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;C&lt;/script&gt; was calculated and thresholded at &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;0.457&lt;/script&gt; (found emperically).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;\begin{align}
    C = \lambda_1\lambda_2-k(\lambda_1+\lambda_2)^2
